description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 41, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 123, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Stringalong for East, Box for South, and Stringalong for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10413-97470-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [123 Votes, Top 15% Score]
